title: 8-9am- A Billboard Record & a New Makeup Trend
itunes:title: 8-9am- A Billboard Record & a New Makeup Trend
description: The show is already off the rails, Sam Smith and Kim Pertas’ Unholy just hit the top of the charts and they break multiple records along the way, Kim Petras becomes the first openly transgender artist to reach number 1 on the hot 100, Katy Pery’s eye glitch, U2 is bummed out because they couldn’t connect with the pop charts, Ed Sheeran is coming out with a documentary, The 5th largest Powerball drawing is tonight, the World Series is on Friday, the newest beauty trend is to do your makeup to look like you were crying, people are being Jeffrey Dahmer for Halloween, a Pizza Place is catching heat for showing what Dahmer’s favorite pizza might look like, a guy was rejected from a job because he was too big, and Vinnie reads your texts!
